wikipedia_page.main: Deji Tobais (born 31 October 1991) is a British male track and field sprinter who competes in the 100 metres and 200 metres. He represented his country at age-category level including two medals at the European Athletics U23 Championships in 2013, where he set a European under-23 record in the 4 × 100 metres relay.
